Calling all pop culture fans! Hot Toys Summer Showcase has kicked off its first stop at Hong Kong yesterday. Have a closer at some of the highly-accurate life-size statues, figure and collectibles that will create an unforgettable experience. Stay tuned as there’s more to come!

#HotToys #SummerShowcase2021

Hot Toys Summer Showcase 2021 @ Hong Kong
Date: 16th JUL – 15th AUG, 2021
Address: Shop G12-14, Fashion Walk, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
Opening Hours: 12:00pm – 9:00pm

node.text:
“It’s time for me to be who I am rather than who I’m supposed to be.” - Thor

Our signature Marvel super hero’s appearance has changed but his heroism remains. Thor is still and always be worthy to wield the mighty hammer, even if he might not necessarily always feel that he is. Today, Hot Toys is excited to present the final product of Thor as 1/6th scale collectible figure from the Avengers: Endgame collection. 

Crafted based on the appearance of Chris Hemsworth’s appearance in the movie, the figure features a newly developed head sculpt with a pair of different colored eyes and specially applied luminous reflective effect that accentuates Thor using his thunder power; a newly developed specialized body that depicts his body with physical changes, expertly tailored body armor with LED light up function and matching lightning effect accessories, signature red-colored cape and body armor, accurate-scaled recreation of LED light up Stormbreaker with impressive details from handle to head, LED light up Mjolnir, pieces of lightning effect accessories, and a figure stand. 

Take a closer look at the God of Thunder now!

#HotToys #Collectibles #SixthScale #Marvel #MarvelStudios #Avengers #Endgame #Thor #ChrisHemsworth

node.text:
“I control the truth… Mysterio is the truth.” - Mysterio

Quentin Beck, a gifted but under-appreciated special effects artist. Chose to focus his skills on becoming Mysterio as the number one super hero in the world, and supplant himself over Iron Man. Coupled with his talent for chemistry, robotics and hypnotism, Mysterio’s convincing illusions on The Elementals blurred the line between reality and fantasy, to the point where the work seems almost supernatural in nature.

Today, Hot Toys is very excited to unveil the final product of Mysterio as 1/6th scale collectible figure from Spider-Man: Far From Home with an additional head sculpt of Quentin Beck!

Skillfully crafted based on the appearance of Jake Gyllenhaal as Quentin Beck, the final figure features a newly developed head sculpt with stunning likeness, a Mysterio helmeted head with LED light up function, finely tailored cape and armors with specially applied luminous reflective patterns, a pair of illusion effect accessories, smoke effect diorama accessories, and a dynamic figure stand.

Mysterio is here to create some illusions! Take a moment to look at the photos taken by our favorite bloggers!

#HotToys #Collectibles #SixthScale #Marvel #MarvelStudios #SMFFH #SpiderManFarFromHome #Mysterio #JakeGyllenhaal

Hot Toys is thrilled to welcome fans to Summer Showcase 2021 to experience this exceptional exhibition on stunningly-accurate collectibles from the highly-anticipated movies to successful live-action series, and action-filled videogames from Marvel, Star Wars, and DC Comics related productions. Highlights include a numerous of finely crafted prototypes and figures, hyper realistic life-size statues, along with the first appearances of Hot Toys Cosbaby Diorama collection.

【RECREATING FAN FAVOURITE CHARACTERS INTO BREATHAKING WORKS】

On entering the atrium of the exhibition, fans will impressed by the life-size statues that are remarkably detailed to the Avengers’ appearances, including Iron Man with Energy Displacer Sentries and Hand Cannon, Iron Patriot with heavy weapons, and Iron Spider reaching out with pincers.

Making its international debut in Hong Kong today, Boba Fett on the Throne as Life Size Statues, inspired by the finale in Star Wars: The Mandalorian, transforming the event ground to a galactic set-up is surely a must-see for any Star Wars fans!

Hot Toys is also sharing a special opportunity with fans to explore the giant version of our most recent Cosbaby Diorama collection, including Venom: Let There Be Carnage, Avengers: Endgame, Star Wars: The Mandalorian, and Toy Story. Have your cameras at the ready and check them out!

Hot Toys Summer Showcase 2021
Date: 16th JUL – 15th AUG, 2021
Address: Shop G12-14, Fashion Walk, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong
Opening Hours: 12:00pm – 9:00pm

BE IMMERSED IN THE #MARVEL UNIVERSE
 
Marvel super heroes are taking over the event ground! Fans can preview the prototypes from Marvel Studios’ blockbusters, featuring 1/6th scale figures of Red Guardian & Black Widow in her most significant black suit from the recently released Black Widow; Spider-Man (Black & Gold Suit) from the upcoming Spider-Man: No Way Home; Iron Strange from Avengers: Endgame (Concept Art Collection); and a diecast version of Iron Man Mark I from the first Iron Man movie. The fan favorite web-slinger Spider-Man in fancy appeals, including Purple Reign Suit, Cyborg Spider-Man Suit and Anti-Ock Suit, based on the action-filled Marvel’s Spider-Man videogame. Fans are also offered a more in-depth view on the Armorized Deadpool from our newly introduced Armorized Warrior Collection, inspired by the character’s origin and appearance in Marvel Comics; as well as the Neon Tech Iron Man 4.0 that gives a neon glow on figure demonstrating Hot Toys incredible craftsmanship.

Hot Toys Summer Showcase 2021
Date: 16th JUL – 15th AUG, 2021
Address: Shop G12-14, Fashion Walk, Causeway Bay, Hong Kong

Tony Stark is gearing up in his suit of technological upgrades to throw back to one of top fan-favorite moments in Iron Man 2. Adding onto the Iron Man collection series, Hot Toys is introducing Iron Man Mark IV with Suit-Up Gantry as stylish Cosbaby. Collectibles measure approximately 10.5 – 14 cm tall with bobble-head function.

Recreates the scene of Tony Stark suits up on the high-tech gantry in his experimental workshop, the latest Cosbaby presents Tony Stark with his arms spreading out, and the gantry assembling him in the Iron Man suit. Includes a specially designed backdrop inspired by Tony’s workshop for diorama setting.

Pick up Hot Toys’ Iron Man Mark IV with Suit-Up Gantry Cosbaby before it’s gone!
